Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.34,0:04:44.79,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5}第二 冲破蛋壳 世界将无限宽广
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.50,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}你扣动正义的扳机
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.46,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}散发异样的情感 让我厌恶
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.85,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H42&}你总是找着悲伤借口
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.85,0:05:05.25,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&H42&}扮演着女主角 让我憎恨
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.37,0:05:09.47,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5\3a&H7E&}泪水根本不适合你吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.87,0:05:13.86,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A2F2&\blur5\3a&H24&\bord2}镜子里真正的我
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.55,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}一事无成且原地踏步
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.08,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}已经无路可走
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.34,0:05:23.93,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}从一开始 我就随波逐流
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.93,0:05:28.35,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}喧嚣环绕在我的四周
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.35,0:05:34.48,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}说着孤独 其实心里早就明白
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.23,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}该告别了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.23,0:05:41.60,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}长久以来 仰望的天空之上
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.60,0:05:46.20,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}望着信仰理想 伸出手去
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.20,0:05:52.16,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}必将有一天 要在万里阴云之下
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.70,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}说出告别
Comment: 1,0:05:54.70,0:05:58.51,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Slash your tears away
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.96,0:06:04.26,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我不会再逃避
